==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fatigate
<hw>Fat"i*gate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To weary; to
tire; to fatigue.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T.
Elyot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

